---
---
<section id="blog" style="background:var(--c-surface)">
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="s-head" data-reveal="up">
            <span class="t-sm">Moving Guides</span>
            <h2 class="t-h2" style="margin-top:14px;margin-bottom:16px">Expert Advice for<br/><em>Smarter Moves.</em></h2>
            <p class="t-body">Practical guides written by our relocation specialists — because a well-planned move is a stress-free move.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-grid">
            <div class="blog-card" data-reveal="up" style="transition-delay:60ms">
                <div class="blog-thumb">📦</div>
                <div class="blog-body">
                    <div class="blog-cat"><span class="chip chip-accent">Packing Guide</span></div>
                    <div class="blog-title">10 Packing Secrets Professional Movers Never Tell You</div>
                    <div class="blog-excerpt">The two-week rule. The weight rule. The colour-coding system. Trade secrets that save hours — and protect your belongings.</div>
                    <div class="blog-meta"><span>📅 Apr 2025</span><span>⏱ 5 min read</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="blog-card" data-reveal="up" style="transition-delay:130ms">
                <div class="blog-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--c-accent),#c0392b)">🚛</div>
                <div class="blog-body">
                    <div class="blog-cat"><span class="chip chip-brand">City Guide</span></div>
                    <div class="blog-title">Moving Hyderabad to Bangalore in 2025: The Complete Checklist</div>
                    <div class="blog-excerpt">Route, cost, timing, what to keep vs what to sell. Everything the software engineer's relocation guide misses.</div>
                    <div class="blog-meta"><span>📅 Mar 2025</span><span>⏱ 8 min read</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="blog-card" data-reveal="up" style="transition-delay:200ms">
                <div class="blog-thumb" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--c-gold),#b7860a)">💰</div>
                <div class="blog-body">
                    <div class="blog-cat"><span class="chip chip-gold">Cost Guide</span></div>
                    <div class="blog-title">What Does House Shifting Actually Cost in South India? (2025)</div>
                    <div class="blog-excerpt">The honest breakdown — 1BHK to villa, local to 700km. What inflates the price. How to get the real number before you commit.</div>
                    <div class="blog-meta"><span>📅 Feb 2025</span><span>⏱ 6 min read</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-actions" data-reveal="up" style="margin-top:44px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="#blog" class="btn btn-outline">View All Articles →</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .blog-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 28px; }
    .blog-card {
        background: var(--c-surface); border-radius: var(--r-xl); overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--c-border); transition: all var(--dur-base) var(--ease-spring);
    }
    .blog-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
    .blog-thumb {
        height: 200px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-brand) 0%, var(--c-brand-2) 100%);
        display: grid; place-items: center; font-size: 56px;
    }
    .blog-thumb::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(10,37,64,.4), transparent); }
    .blog-body { padding: 28px; }
    .blog-cat { margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .blog-title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--c-ink); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.35; }
    .blog-excerpt { font-size: 14px; color: var(--c-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .blog-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--c-faint); }

    @media(max-width:1100px) { .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
    @media(max-width:720px) { .blog-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
